tofu meatballs
via Judy Heumann

tofu meatballs

1 container (12oz.) tofu - drained and mashed
3 slices toast and crumble
1/2 c chopped onion
3 eggs lightly beaten
3 tbsp parmesan cheese
1 tbsp mustard
1/4 tsp each basil, rosemary, garlic, pepper
1/8 tsp nutmeg

In a large bowl combine all ingredients and mix.
Heat oil or butter in a pan
Spoon mixture into pan like patties.
Brown on both sides (10-15 min)